                     <interp inst="t18180909-136-person1119" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. On the 22d of July I searched the prisoner at Mr. Earith's, and found the duplicates of the property on him.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I intended to redeem them.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 32.</p>
